Poisons (Midwifery Substances) Amendment Order 2016

I make the following order under section 3 of the Poisons Act 1971 .

2 November 2016

MICHAEL DARREL JOSEPH FERGUSON

Minister for Health

1. Short title
    This order may be cited as the Poisons (Midwifery Substances) Amendment Order 2016 .

2. Commencement
    This order takes effect on the day on which its making is notified in the Gazette.

3. Principal Order
    In this order, the Poisons (Midwifery Substances) Order 2011 is referred to as the Principal Order.

4.
    The amendments effected by this clause have been incorporated into the authorised version of the Poisons (Midwifery Substances) Order 2011 .

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 16 November 2016

This order is administered in the Department of Health and Human Services.
